nodes.text: Moahdi was a male Melida from Melida/Daan. He was part of a sniper task force led by Wehutti. The other members of the task force were Herut and Kejas. While waiting for emissaries from the Jedi Temple to arrive, Moahdi and the task force attacked Jedi Knights Qui-Gon Jinn and Obi-Wan Kenobi, mistaking them for Daan enemies instead of their Jedi contacts.
